## Buying a Computer

In Unit 1, Day 3-4, students investigate the components of a computer and decide which components will be more important to each user.

#### Suggested Resources

Here is a good resource that explains the internal components of a computer in detail. Take a few minutes to look through it - you may want to use it in your classroom. 

<strong><a href="http://www.carnegiecyberacademy.com/facultyPages/computer/computers.html" target="_blank">Computer Hardware - by Carnegie Mellon University >></a></strong>

You may want to keep the site open, because in the next level, we will present a sample assessment about the different components of a computer.

